{"tid":1454042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］和理非行動一定要配合升級","createTime":"2019-08-12T06:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:38:19.000Z","uid":54550,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"352f6590edb455ab08a5fb61a638ebe66be6570d","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"運動發展到今日，和理非既行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對需要配合升級</span></span>。<br />\n每星期我地都損失寶貴既手足，<br />\n 勇敢既前線兄弟苦苦堅持。<br />\n唔敢上前其實亦係人之常情，但我地撫心自問，係咪可以用自己既方向做到更多，至少<span style=\"color: red;\">為前線兄弟爭取喘息空間同輿論支持</span>，等佢地可以放心爬山？<br />\n<br />\n示威者一方應該開始<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">改變心態</span></span>，<br />\n諗方法爭取<span style=\"color: red;\">更多民意基礎</span>。<br />\n要食埋對家個餅，<br />\n或者<span style=\"color: red;\">至少令佢地食唔倒</span>。<br />\n感化唔倒至少都要俾佢地多一個角度睇件事，<br />\n絕對會令輿論風向再有改變。<br />\n<br />\n不如我地逆向思考，以後生仔抗爭者名義，<br />\n搞啲又<span style=\"color: red;\">利民又做到文宣</span>嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n呢度拋磚引玉先，呢期經濟生意麻麻地，<br />\n好多人話基層手停口停，<br />\n我地就以牙還牙，學民建聯咁搞派米/月餅，<br />\n以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「政府只搞大白象，自己人民後生救」</span></span>之類嘅名義，<br />\n搞<span style=\"color: red;\">社區服務活動</span>，排隊位就搞<span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭真相放映</span>，<br />\n反正有排排隊，班人有聲有畫點會唔睇？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再令我地被屈死係社會破壞者嘅身分</span></span>，<br />\n和理非一齊搞社會服務同時文宣，<br />\n拿最多嘅道德輿論<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畀前線去運用</span></span>，<br />\n等佢地無咁多後顧之憂。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家又出下計仔，和理非，你地ready好升級未？<br />\n勿忘五大訴求，<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不指責，香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1881c339f854858486381f6e6b332c0e788336d4","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:06:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3665a8be201118a828d0394c043bd4e8a9e639a8","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b118dda44251b8081edce01117506cb7e308fbf","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:11:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b13ebf1327fd34a89f851b72fa45ba7acaa8b40b","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f023cd78a2831c41e2c9cdc097a16ec5c4114b16","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38b4a9fc89649c6ad1e10194fa4a16fdc0619b97","tid":1454042,"uid":17133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615587dd7b79ea0dafafb4a0c43574f43f349e93","tid":1454042,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bF2GCic.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbF2GCic.png&h=84b031c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nur0SRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnur0SRy.png&h=953d238f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qk0dtpU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQk0dtpU.png&h=9dfe3bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWJq3Yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWJq3Yf.png&h=513b9d97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pxJYg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pxJYg.png&h=46368cde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YWL3Yh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YWL3Yh.png&h=3fa2c3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZ9BrbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZ9BrbD.png&h=434c987d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"732ab5ad89d46618ac3ff2063759fdc8474d7ac0","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"歡迎大家一齊諗計，<br />\n繼續淨係不合作同埋fb 文宣真係唔夠，<br />\n我地好需要用和理非既方式升級，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">配合前線雙管齊下</span></span>"},{"pid":"dc7d4b66c58cc9daaa361788b36c2d04b300c93e","tid":1454042,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:29:50.000Z","msg":"[替天行道]你奪去我們的光明，我們送你入無盡的黑暗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1454138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1454138</a>"},{"pid":"0be53b4d1bc243cf84d1405b74ce4f50ec36968c","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:37:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5c11bb16fe147b3b8c35b6e3a4f80de54f8f230","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:47:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4530808d0335eb0ca577975181a27fa5775c48d1","tid":1454042,"uid":100224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"短期內要搞一次和理非機場大集會，唔衝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n1. 抗爭兩個月後做一次民意統計<br />\n2. 設定deadline要求回應<br />\n3. Deadline唔回應升級全面大罷工十日<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n<br />\n1. 勇武既效能大幅降低，612衝同而家衝已經完全唔同<br />\n<br />\n2. 勇武再升級前，要用和理非最暴力去對抗，同時罷工果日唔可以衝，最多塞地鐵，將焦點放係罷工到<br />\n<br />\n3. 罷工前要宣言，遊行集會set deadline會係好方法<br />\n<br />\n4. 罷工要時間醞釀，所以集會呢段時間會係一個好既時間<br />\n<br />\n困難：<br />\n<br />\n1. 不反對通知書唔會批，同樣會暴力清場，唔會和平得去邊<br />\n<br />\n2. 黑警如果扮示威者衝，個focus又會變左衝，而唔係罷工<br />\n<br />\n解決方法（歡迎更多）<br />\n<br />\n1. 文宣以和理非為主調宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 口以相傳，提醒勇武人士忍忍手先，罷工完再郁手<br />\n<br />\n3. 將集會擺係機場附近進行，令班狗唔可以暴力清場<br />\n<br />\n4. 未諗到"},{"pid":"cbe9564b660b7a4eae666de732db2f7ffe368273","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4717e7a4342c36aa04296d028da1892b28f94aab","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d0cfe8aba47ff67cd0664317f06a3fe93dfd5b5","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cc836727600cd4f7c9b141791718562b6fa29b20","tid":1454042,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">係林鄭將香港推向一個萬劫不復的深淵<br />\n係林鄭月娥忍心將香港推進粉身碎骨深淵</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"51971206edcb5b732e7be4a9133ff690076be12f","tid":1454042,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"bc02f65c111e1239397007e435257987715a24ed","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09f9bbcec624a4616df6b09019a159021134d6e5","tid":1454042,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6f029a85b2237f3b4cfba0948e08acd4d865ef98","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:31:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"876d4ac619789f873df4bf229f082175908e39c2","tid":1454042,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ffe49599fcdd3c43766a102bc17c871ac2dd169a","tid":1454042,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:38:19.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}